-------------------------------------LINUX METHOD-------------------------------------------------------------

1) Go into the diretory where you hold your header_file, malloc_new.c file and yout main.c file using terminal.
2) run the following commands
	->	gcc malloc_new.h malloc_new.c main.c -o mall
	->	./mall


-------------------------------------WINDOWS METHOD------------------------------------------------------------
1) Downlod and install 'minGW'
2) Go to the direcory where you hold your files using Command Prompt.
2) run the following commands
	->	gcc malloc_new.h malloc_new.c main.c -o mall.exe
	->	mall.exe


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


** and you can edit the main.c file as you wish
